creator: Appspace
descriptionHtml:
Keeping everyone on the same page is no simple task. A modern workforce is continuously on the go, always switched on, and expects to know what is going on at all times.

The Appspace App makes the right information available to the right people, at the right time. And because our app is compatible with so many devices your information can be shared anywhere.

Enable your teams to instantly access information from their Android devices. They simply log in, browse, and view. View sales reports, product specs, training videos, technical support trends, HR messages, and more – even information from other corporate systems.

Don't have Appspace? Learn more and set up an account at www.appspace.com.
descriptionShort: Get instant access to your Appspace channels on your Android device.
